{"tid":892923,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"🚨🚨🚨［箍牙］所有幫襯緊葉宇焜（牙醫）嘅手足一定要入一入嚟！","createTime":"2018-11-07T08:28:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T13:43:03.000Z","uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a55a657ac76a049f42050d8107f45b2795349c52","tid":892923,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T08:28:21.000Z","msg":"之前一路都覺得奇怪<br />\n點解可以隔半年先覆診<br />\n<br />\n據佢地診所 所講 佢地係要執咗間分店<br />\n所以要半年之後先去第間覆診<br />\n之後一直都冇下文<br />\n橡筋、牙蠟嗰啲亦都冇俾<br />\n<br />\n最近覺得勁奇怪<br />\n於是Google下佢個名<br />\n發現下面呢個po<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">原來佢已經死咗</span></span></strong><br />\n詳情大家自己入去睇下<br />\n資料都幾零碎<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>有冇人喺佐敦葉宇焜到箍過牙？<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/btiFtS\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/btiFtS</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲知多少少可以講下？<br />\n<br />\n呢個po主要係提醒返<br />\n同我一樣唔知道佢死咗嘅巴絲打"},{"pid":"94b055bb15db04a0b9436b96bbbc8c90a1ad3203","tid":892923,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T08:31:14.000Z","msg":"最近睇返先知原來條友真係幾唔掂<br />\n個名都幾衰下<br />\n求其Google都見到一大堆係鬧佢嘅"},{"pid":"491f980354153edaef855d949a168deaa90efdf3","tid":892923,"uid":137233,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T08:40:09.000Z","msg":"牙你老母"},{"pid":"ee20e70f52b3df9838e70be7fdfc658718cc99cb","tid":892923,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"491f980354153edaef855d949a168deaa90efdf3","tid":892923,"uid":137233,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T08:40:09.000Z","msg":"牙你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T08:48:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b3cf1eacd9835bcfc680ff04a2f2ddada0aadd","tid":892923,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T09:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd94163